<!-- Node: "Gearbox Hiring Level Designers & Artists" -->
<div class="body_box_header">Gearbox Hiring Level Designers & Artists</div>
<div class="body_box"><small>Submitted by <a href="http://www.gamedesign.net/user/view/1804" title="View user profile.">Kingpin_Xatrix</a> on Thursday, April 8, 2004 - 12:08</small><br /><br />
<b>GearBox</b> is looking for a 2d Texture Artist, 3d Artist, Game Test Lead/IT Spport and Level Designer. All of the jobs available for a full-time. Visit their <a href = "http://www.gearboxsoftware.com/employment.html">website</a> for full info.
